@startuml name

title  Επιλογή Λίστας Αναπαραγωγής

actor User
participant HomeView
participant HomeController
participant PlaylistView
participant PlaylistController
participant Playlist
participant Song
participant SongControllerAPI
participant SongService
participant SongRepository
participant PlaylistControllerAPI
participant PlaylistService
participant PlaylistRepository
activate HomeController
HomeController -> HomeView : display()
activate HomeView
User -> HomeView : showPlaylists()
HomeView -> HomeController : showPlaylist()
deactivate HomeView
HomeController -> PlaylistController : getPlaylists()
deactivate HomeController
activate PlaylistController

PlaylistController -> Playlist : requestPlaylists()
activate Playlist
'async Διότι μπορεί να παίζει ήδη κάποιο playlist και να μην χρειάζεται να αναβληθεί η αναπαραγωγή των τραγουδιών για να κάνει fetch τα άλλα playlists
Playlist ->> PlaylistControllerAPI : sendHTTPrequest()
PlaylistControllerAPI ->> PlaylistService : proccessHTTPRequest()
PlaylistService ->> PlaylistRepository : runQuery()
PlaylistRepository --> PlaylistService : return results
PlaylistService --> PlaylistControllerAPI : return results
PlaylistControllerAPI --> Playlist : return results
Playlist --> PlaylistController : return Playlists
PlaylistController -> PlaylistView : showPlaylists()
activate PlaylistView
User -> PlaylistView : selectPlaylist()
PlaylistView -> PlaylistController : getPlaylistSongs()
PlaylistController -> Song : getSongs()
activate Song
Song ->> SongControllerAPI : sendHTTPRequest()
SongControllerAPI ->> SongService : processHTTPRequest()
SongService ->> SongRepository : runQuery()
SongRepository --> SongService : return Songs
SongService --> SongControllerAPI : return Songs
SongControllerAPI --> Song : return Songs
Song --> Playlist : return Songs
Playlist --> PlaylistController : return Songs
PlaylistController -> PlaylistView : showSelectedPlaylist()

@enduml